{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-timeline-js","path":"/RyanNielson/awesome-unity/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"awesomeList":{"repo":"RyanNielson/awesome-unity","descriptionHTML":"<div>A curated list of awesome Unity assets, resources, and more.</div>","description":"A curated list of awesome Unity assets, resources, and more."},"awesomeListMeta":{"readmeParsedAt":"2021-06-29T11:26:59.447Z"},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://nielson.dev/2015/12/splatter-effects-in-unity-using-the-stencil-buffer\">2D Splatter Effects Using the Stencil Buffer</a> - Using the stencil buffer in Unity to draw splatter effects on surfaces. This could be used for paint or blood splatter.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-04-26T13:02:22.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://nielson.dev/2015/10/fixing-gaps-between-sprites-better-2d-in-unity-part-2\">Fixing Gaps Between Sprites</a> - A short tutorial about removing the small gaps that sometimes appear between adjacent sprites.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-04-26T13:02:22.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>2D</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/sprite-management/2d-rope-system-17722\">2D Rope System (Paid)</a> - Scripts for creating any type of 2D ropes in the editor or during runtime.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>2D</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/level-design/ferr2d-terrain-tool-11653\">Ferr2D Terrain Tool (Paid)</a> - Quickly create handcrafted 2D landscapes and levels.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>2D</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/characters/anima2d-no-longer-supported-replaced-by-2d-animation-79840\">Unity Anima2D</a> - Advanced skeletal animation editor with support for both per-object and skinned mesh animation with an integrated in-editor skinning tool.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Augmented &#x26; Virtual Reality</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/integration/vrtk-virtual-reality-toolkit-vr-toolkit-64131\">SteamVR Unity Toolkit</a> - Scripts and Great examples to abstract the use of VR controller actions in Unity.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Camera</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/templates/systems/ufps-ultimate-fps-2943\">UFPS (Paid)</a> - Provides camera, controllers, and other effects for use in FPS games.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Monetization</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/add-ons/services/unity-monetization-66123\">Unity Monetization</a> - Unity Ads is a video ad network with quick and seamless integration using regular and opt-in ads.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Networking</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/network/nakama-81338\">Nakama</a> - Build social and realtime games with an open-source <a href=\"https://github.com/heroiclabs/nakama\">distributed server</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/heroiclabs/nakama\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.6k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4613,\"repo\":\"heroiclabs/nakama\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Networking</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/network/photon-bolt-free-127156\">Photon Bolt (Paid)</a> - Build networked games without having to know the details of networking or write any complex networking code.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Networking</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/network/photon-unity-networking-classic-free-1786\">Photon Unity Networking</a> - Plug and play cloud networking that also works for local hosting. Free for up to 20 concurrent users.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Scripting</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/input-management/easy-save-the-complete-save-load-asset-768\">Easy Save 2 (Paid)</a> - A fast and simple way to save and load data on all major platforms supported by Unity.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Scripting</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/particles-effects/unistorm-volumetric-clouds-sky-modular-weather-and-cloud-shadows-2714\">UniStorm (Paid)</a> - A customizable dynamic day and night weather system that creates realistic storms and weather.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Services</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/UnityAnalyticsSetup.html\">Unity Analytics</a> - Provides a dashboard with metrics to help track active players, sessions, retention, and revenue.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tweening</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/animation/dotween-hotween-v2-27676\">DOTween</a> - Tween any numeric property or field (including Vectors, Rectangles, etc.), plus some non-numeric ones (like strings). This is the follow-up to HOTween.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tweening</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/animation/itween-84\">iTween</a> - A simple, and easy to use animation system.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tweening</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/animation/leantween-3595\">LeanTween</a> - FOSS, and also the most lightweight tweening library for Unity. Allows you to tween any value you have access to via the .value() method.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>UI</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/gui/ngui-next-gen-ui-2413\">NGUI (Paid)</a> - A powerful UI system and event notification framework.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>UI</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://docs.unity3d.com/Packages/com.unity.textmeshpro@1.3/manual/index.html\">TextMesh Pro</a> - A alternative to render text in uGUI by using the distance field technique, which allows crisp fonts at any scale. This was recently purchased by Unity and will be integrated into the engine in the future.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Utilities</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/utilities/grouping-tool-147552\">Grouping Tool</a> - Easily group objects together</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Utilities</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/level-design/snazzygrid2-19245\">SnazzyGrid (Paid)</a> - Makes it easy to manage positions of assets in the scene with easy to use snapping tools and many more features to improve the scene creation workflow.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Utilities</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/version-control/unimerge-9733\">UniMerge (Paid)</a> - Editor extension for merging scenes and prefabs, also integrates with VCS.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Visual Scripting</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/visual-scripting/playmaker-368\">Playmaker (Paid)</a> - Quickly make gameplay prototypes, A.I. behaviors, animation graphs, interactive objects, and more using finite state machines.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-25T10:26:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>AI</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/ai/apex-path-17943\">Apex Path (Paid)</a> - Apex Path handles dynamic pathfinding including local avoidance steering and dynamic obstacles.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-12-01T13:05:07.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tips and Tricks</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Unity-Technologies/SuperScience\">Unity Labs' Super Science</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Unity-Technologies/SuperScience\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">466</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":466,\"repo\":\"Unity-Technologies/SuperScience\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Gems of Unity Labs for user education.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-08-24T16:10:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Frameworks</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/visual-scripting/uframe-game-framework-14381\">uFrame (Paid)</a> - Create maintainable games faster, better, more stable, a